## Limitations

The research is limited by the availability of up-to-date information and the potential bias in sources that promote ethical hacking as a career. Additionally, the scope of this report is confined to the general benefits and necessity of ethical hacking, without delving into specific case studies or technical methodologies. Further research could explore the impact of ethical hacking on specific industries or its role in regulatory compliance.